'''Slayer Equipment''' shops are run by [[Slayer master]]s. They consist of various tools and weapons for use against [[Slayer monsters]].

All shops share the same stock.

Items required for the player's current [[Slayer task]] are highlighted in the shop interface.

==Locations==
*[[Burthorpe]]
*[[Draynor Village]]
